data.title: Why Spectral Normalization Stabilizes GANs: Analysis and Improvements
data.description: Figure 1: Training instability is one of the biggest challenges in training GANs. Despite the existence of successful heuristics like Spectral Normalization (SN) for improving stability, it is poorly-understood why they work. In our research, we theoretically explain why SN stabilizes GAN training.
